      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    How to move goods through RORO locations in a no deal Brexit: EU to UK and UK to EU
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Process flow for freight roll-on, roll-off (RORO) imports and exports between the UK and the EU for a no-deal Brexit (excluding Northern Ireland).</p>

  </div>
</div>

