<div class="call-to-action">
<h2 id="stay-up-to-date">Stay up to date</h2>

<p>The <abbr title="United Kingdom">UK</abbr> will leave the <abbr title="European Union">EU</abbr> on 31 October. This page tells you how to prepare for Brexit. It will be updated if anything changes, including if a deal is agree.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/government/brexit">Sign up for email alerts</a> to get the latest information.</p>
</div>

<h2 id="download-the-pocket-guide">Download the pocket guide</h2>

<p>The information in the downloadable pocket guide is the same as the information on this web page. Download the pocket guide if you want to save or print a copy of the information.</p>

